### go-sunabar-payments API リクエスト集
# VS Code REST Client や JetBrains の HTTP Client で開いて使う想定。
# 変数は環境ごとに `@base` を書き換える。

@base = http://localhost:8080
@accountId = ACC0001
@appReqId = local-{{$timestamp}}

### Health check
GET {{base}}/healthz

### Metrics ( Outbox / Transfer 集計 )
GET {{base}}/metrics
Accept: application/json

### Sync accounts ( sunabar から取得して DB へ反映 )
POST {{base}}/accounts/sync

### List accounts
GET {{base}}/accounts

### Get balance
GET {{base}}/accounts/{{accountId}}/balance

### Issue virtual account
POST {{base}}/virtual-accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "memo": "invoice-001",
  "expiresOn": "2027-12-31"
}

### List virtual accounts
GET {{base}}/virtual-accounts

### Request transfer ( appRequestId で冪等性を担保 )
POST {{base}}/transfers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appRequestId": "{{appReqId}}",
  "amount": 1500,
  "sourceAccountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "destBankCode": "0033",
  "destBranchCode": "001",
  "destAccountType": "1",
  "destAccountNum": "1234567",
  "destAccountName": "ヤマダ タロウ"
}

### Get transfer status ( 上記レスポンスの id を埋める )
GET {{base}}/transfers/<TRANSFER_ID>

### 同一 appRequestId で再送 -> 同じ id が返る ( 冪等 )
POST {{base}}/transfers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appRequestId": "{{appReqId}}",
  "amount": 1500,
  "sourceAccountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "destBankCode": "0033",
  "destBranchCode": "001",
  "destAccountType": "1",
  "destAccountNum": "1234567",
  "destAccountName": "ヤマダ タロウ"
}
